name: V15_19.1.2.3
descriptionHtml:
Display Rules for Surgical Parameter Modals.
Verify the Surgical Parameter Modals are used to change the values of the associated surgical functions. The Surgical Parameter Modals appear when a Surgical Parameter Button is touched:
- Surgical Modal with Slider Control: Min/Max Value Label, Adjustment Arrows Buttons, Slider Control
- Surgical Modal without Slider Control
statusMessage: "1st point color above Dynamic Graphic Limit Line" color || Expected - Color [A=255, R=27, G=41, B=57] +/-5, Actual - Color [A=255, R=0, G=0, B=0].
